'''Cologne''' was a pleasant scent that [[Sentience/Legends|sentients]] applied to themselves. This was often used to cover bad smells.<ref name="df:sote">''[[Dark Forces: Soldier for the Empire]]''</ref> Different brands existed, such as [[Tauntaun Splash-On Cologne]]<ref name="swa">''[[Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance]]''</ref> and [[Hapan cologne]].<ref name="t">''[[Legacy of the Force: Tempest]]''</ref>

A [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]], [[Slyder]], applied cologne to cover his strong [[Pheromone/Legends|pheromones]].<ref name="df:sote" /> [[Vor]] [[Senator/Legends|senator]] [[Fyg Boras]] of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] wore cologne with a [[Mint/Legends|mint]] scent.

